{"tid":407942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為持BNO三萬港人爭取番英籍肥彭話同上議院傾傾","createTime":"2017-09-20T23:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T16:17:55.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8164e8e11158f2f751e5d6d8fc5198c28b02bcdb","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T23:37:49.000Z","msg":"隔牆有耳：爭取BNO變英籍？<br />\n肥彭話同上議院傾傾 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n肥彭連日安排午餐會見各界人士，香港政界對肥彭亦相當捧場，場場座無虛席，好似噚日民主政制促進聯委會為肥彭搞嘅午餐會，民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、民主黨前主席劉慧卿都有到場，馬丁見到肥彭，讚肥彭瘦咗好多，亦比佢上一次來港精神得多，馬丁又自嘲自己腰圍50年不變！肥彭就講想自己腰圍同馬丁一樣，不過肥彭咁為食，怕且都好難！<br />\n至於卿姐見到肥彭，就不忘為香港人發聲，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">卿姐噚日話同肥彭講，叫佢要為持英國海外公民護照（BNO）嘅3萬個港人發聲，向英國政府爭取番英國國籍！</span></span>肥彭好客氣，笑言可在上議院提出，但大家都知上議院權力有限。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;<br />\nBNO本來就係英籍？<br />\n持BNO港人點止3萬?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0b176c878a4c08cf8dea3196427e9f4ee33cb4","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T23:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c383500a6582195162770678edffc73581564f","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T23:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3f95ff760dd6192ad26e76d15b88a712b933e4","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c905a800b8f9ea0320ed3ca14f52fd05ae0009","tid":407942,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:35:26.000Z","msg":"真識講笑"},{"pid":"4395c48291cd96ec257887d51e0468c9850f73c5","tid":407942,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"發夢啦"},{"pid":"8f9d59cf5ac18b5540fc7c17138e15a5dfda4fc6","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"bno只係旅遊證件 <br />\n唔係英籍？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea42d4cd4bd36442e64ec303e7df43e01ef53273","tid":407942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac78dca8d4e097c7882b0b1b8d783fb64e7b4d5","tid":407942,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"得三萬?"},{"pid":"9f85e01d9643e906b17ac375d21fedd59f88de03","tid":407942,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}